{
  "stem": "17515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only men, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I saw-- I been-- after change commando, I'd been working as a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dug-- That mean repairing roof, put new roof on the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to the gypsy barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to the-- woman barracks, separated from the gypsy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gypsy used to live in the Birkenau, whole family, with the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With like 10, 12, 15 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the family, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, the German deliver them for the children, milk and white bread, by purpose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a couple days, everybody go to gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we been talking about gas chamber, crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So to me, they was scared by even looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the nighttime, Birkenau, there was a-- a smoke come from a chimney with-- with the-- white [INAUDIBLE] spark.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the smell, there was an odor from the-- from the bone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Daytime, nighttime.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That crematorium was working 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- I-- I spoke with the-- I believe it was not allowed, Polish-Jewish who work in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're calling sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew what-- what going to happen to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a couple months I say, we have to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to pick up fresh people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nice-looking people, young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were some very young, nice people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kanada, and there was people who pick up-- yes, leave the jewelry, money on the side, the clothes on the other side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's called Kanada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, in Kanada, they're calling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Kanada, that was people will-- will pick-- pick up the clothes and jewelry, separate it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I mean, many, many of them-- they-- they stole the jewelry, mostly the SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The black market was in Auschwitz, I'll tell you true.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
